This post is being bumped in answer to the suggestion that everyone (or a large percentage of people) now dislike TLC.  If you think all these people have changed their minds in the past few weeks that's fine, obviously I won't be able to change anyone's mind.  But really, it's human nature.  People who have an axe to grind are far more vocal than those who like things the way they are.  Just let Verant hint they actually are considering removing TLC wholesale (other than the minor modifications I believe would help it) and see what happens.  Until then, I think the silent and content majority will remain just that: silent.<br>
