<br>
Ok &lt;takes a deep breath&gt;...<br>
<br>
My apologies if I have been coming across to aggresively about TLC. I'd like to explain why I feel so strongly about it if you'll just bear with me.<br>
<br>
I do feel very strongly about TLC (just incase you didn't notice that). I was one of the folks that started the campaign many months ago to remove or modifiy the TLC on production servers (blue/regular ruleset etc). It was a very difficult process and we were very proud that we were successful.<br>
<br>
Soooo, what the heck am I doing on FV if I am so against TLC? Why don't I just go play somewhere else? Well, I mentioned in another post I always consider the good with the bad and when I decided to play on FV I decided there was enough &quot;good&quot; to outweigh what I thought was &quot;bad&quot;. In fact, I think the TLC is the only thing I don't like about this server.<br>
<br>
We used the same type of logic to defeat TLC many months ago. The bad points about it outweigh the good. Mind you, good and bad are relative so obviously not everyone will agree. I hope this gives you folks some insight as to why I feel the way I do about this issue. Once again apologise if I came across to aggresively.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
